item.title: The RETHINKING European Offices 2030
item.description: The RETHINKING European Offices 2030 report examines office stock across 16 key European cities and the opportunities for landlords to reposition or repurpose their space. By 2030, Cushman & Wakefield estimates that more than 170 million sqm of office stock is at risk in 16 European cities. This is equivalent to more than six times the total office stock in Central London.
